{"tid":1896761,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"屌閪 頭先同啲fd講有睇全職高手 比佢哋打到牙都甩","createTime":"2020-02-25T10:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T23:26:49.000Z","uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5306d7a2fb31775a6259e755737ec9cd3d48385e","tid":1896761,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"頭先同班好耐冇見既fd食飯<br />\n講起打機 我問吓佢哋有冇睇套講打機既動漫<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢哋：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋：刀劍神域牙嘛有睇<br />\n我：唔係牙 講電競個套呢 叫全職高手啊<br />\n佢哋成班開始發老脾係咁屌鳩我睇支那野又盛<br />\n講咩反送中咁耐仲睇支那野<br />\n<br />\n我都唔好意思出聲<br />\n過左陣佢地玩手機game<br />\n見到佢哋玩個隻好撚毒既碧藍航線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我又癮唔住講：你哋咪又有玩大game<br />\n佢哋話：你唔好道德綁架 同埋我哋玩日服架 隻game全日文架<br />\n我又話：咪又係會比支那政府抽稅整飛彈打香港 係到雙重標準 全職高手夠有日文版啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢成去面都紅哂 我就繼續食野<br />\n佢哋嬲都停哂手 食食下有個忍唔住氣冇啦啦一拳車埋黎<br />\n打到我隻門牙鬆鬆地<br />\n好彩比啲員工撳住左佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f48605e6ef5b9ee69a60261c32d3d64170a0fe2","tid":1896761,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(10/10)<br />\n黎sir好波"},{"pid":"755aef9e4cb1d183b5dfb949d5c1cdc544a0f546","tid":1896761,"uid":167721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"你都係想問邊到有平嘅牙醫睇啫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edr.hk/dentist/info/lau-wai-man-b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edr.hk%2Fdentist%2Finfo%2Flau-wai-man-b&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQ2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=659460b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edr.hk/dentist/info/lau-wai-man-b</a